					<description><![CDATA[<p>Press Release Date: March 1, 2024 New Leadership at CM Hammar AB, Starting April 1, 2024 Gothenburg, Sweden - CM Hammar AB, a world leader in maritime safety, announces the appointment of Mattias Malmgren as CEO partnering a co-leadership model with Anna Hultberg as COO, effective April 1, 2024. This leadership change marks a strategic...</p>
